metadata.name: The MERGE
metadata.description: PIPS is a first-of its kind NFT that contains an entire deck of playing cards in one NFT that can be used in metaverse gaming for PIPS games like Skirmish and Poker. Each NFT contains 57 custom SVG image assets: 52 playing cards, 2 jokers, 1 card back design, 1 ad card, and 1 box design — all of which can be viewed on pipcards.com. “The MERGE” deck is a tribute to the Ethereum protocol commemorating the integration of proof of stake with 3,333 limited edition custom Ethereum decks.
